# --- FiveM & Server Artifacts ---
# Ignore the temporary server cache 
**/fivem-server-files/cache/

# Ignore the server binaries/core files 
# These should be downloaded/updated via artifacts, not versioned.
**/fxserver/

# Ignore local server data and logs [cite: 348]
**/txData/

# --- Web / Frontend (stdb-inventory/web) ---
# Ignore dependencies 
**/node_modules/
# Ignore production builds [cite: 189]
**/web/dist/

# --- Rust / SpacetimeDB Modules ---
# Ignore all compilation artifacts [cite: 312]
target/

# --- .NET (stdb-sidecar) ---
# Ignore build outputs and temporary object files [cite: 346, 347]
stdb-sidecar/bin/
stdb-sidecar/obj/

# --- IDE & System ---
# Optional: Ignore local editor history, though you may want to keep .cursor/rules [cite: 311, 312]
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
